---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About PulseLab - Privacy-First Women's Health" description="Learn about PulseLab's mission to build privacy-first women's health apps. We believe your health data is yours alone.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-8">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="section-label">About Us</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-6">
          Privacy-First Women's Health
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-[var(--text-medium)]">
          Building apps that respect your data, your privacy, and your body.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-8 bg-white">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-[var(--text-medium)] space-y-6">
        <p>
          PulseLab was founded with a simple belief: <strong>your health data is yours alone</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          In an era where period tracking apps share intimate data with advertisers and social networks
          monetize your health information, we chose a different path. We build apps that work entirely
          on your device, with zero data collection, zero cloud uploads, and zero compromises.
        </p>
        <p>
          We focus specifically on women's health because we believe this space deserves better.
          Women deserve apps that respect their privacy, especially when tracking something as personal
          as menstrual cycles, perimenopause symptoms, or fertility windows.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-8 bg-[var(--bg-light)]">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-6">Our Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[var(--gradient)] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-2">Privacy by Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--text-medium)]">
              We don't just promise privacy — we build it into the foundation. Our apps physically
              cannot share your data because they never connect to our servers. We can't see your
              data, can't sell your data, and never have your data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[var(--gradient)] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/>
              <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-2">Honest Business Model</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--text-medium)]">
              When an app is free, you're the product. We charge a fair, one-time price for our
              apps. No subscriptions draining your wallet, no ads interrupting your experience,
              no premium tiers holding features hostage.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[var(--gradient)] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-2">Quality Over Quantity</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--text-medium)]">
              We'd rather build one exceptional app than ten mediocre ones. Every feature,
              every screen, every interaction is considered. We take the time to do things right.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-8 bg-white">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-6">Our Products</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--bg-light)] border border-[rgba(0,180,160,0.1)]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--primary)] to-[var(--accent)] flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8">
                <path d="M8 32 L18 32 L26 12 L30 52 L34 20 L38 44 L42 12 L46 52 L50 32 L56 32" stroke="white" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)]">Sync</h3>
              <p class="text-[var(--accent)] italic">Find your peak.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-medium)] mb-4">
            A privacy-first cycle tracker that predicts your peak days for intimacy.
            Works completely offline, never requires an account, and keeps all your data
            on your device.
          </p>
          <a href="/sync" class="text-[var(--primary)] font-semibold hover:underline">Learn more about Sync →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--ember-bg)] border border-[rgba(212,88,58,0.1)]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <img src="/ember/icon.png" alt="Ember" class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--ember-text)]">Ember</h3>
              <p class="text-[var(--ember-accent)] italic">Your body, illuminated.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-medium)] mb-4">
            Track perimenopause and menopause symptoms, discover patterns in your health data,
            and generate PDF reports for your healthcare provider — all without sharing a
            single byte of your data.
          </p>
          <a href="/ember" class="text-[var(--ember-primary)] font-semibold hover:underline">Learn more about Ember →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-8 bg-[var(--text-dark)] text-white">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
        Have questions, feedback, or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@pulselab.cc" class="btn btn-primary inline-flex">
        Contact Us
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose strong {
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
</style>
